Description:
============
    Creates a new view component, test and preview files.
    Pass the component name, either CamelCased or under_scored, and an optional list of attributes as arguments.

Example:
========
    bin/rails generate view_component Gravatar email size

    creates a Gravatar component and test:
        Component:    app/views/components/component_library/gravatar/component.rb
        Template:     app/views/components/component_library/gravatar/component.html.erb
        Test:         test/views/components/component_library/gravatar_component_test.rb
        Preview:      app/views/components/component_library/gravatar/component_preview.rb
        JS:           app/views/components/component_library/gravatar/component.js
        CSS:          app/views/components/component_library/gravatar/component.css
